// Man page for active
manActive="ACTIVE(1)                        X Shell Manual                        ACTIVE(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    active - Show active network interface
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>active</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Shows the currently active network interface. Displays which network
    adapter is currently handling network traffic.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <b>active</b>
    Display active network interface
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>ifconfig</b>, <b>iwconfig</b>"